Sharespot 是一个用于生成美观的网页文本分享图像的工具。
- 只需选择文本，点击鼠标右键，选择 "share by Sharespot"，然后就可以看到内容预览卡片；
- 点击右上角“电源键”或者按下“esc”键即可关闭分享预览；
- 点击“拍照”按钮，即可将预览卡片生成为图片，可点击图片放大查看或复制、下载等；
- 该图像将包含由源页面 URL 生成的二维码，接收你分享的图像的人可以通过扫描二维码轻松访问源页面。

Sharespot is a tool designed to generate attractive web text share images.
- Simply select the text, right-click, and choose "share by Sharespot" to see a content preview card;
- Click the "power button" in the top right corner or press the "esc" key to close the share preview;
- Click the "camera" button to turn the preview card into an image, which you can enlarge for a - better view or copy and download, etc.;
- The image will include a QR code generated from the source page URL, allowing anyone who receives your shared image to easily access the original page by scanning the QR code.
